          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">AN EPIGRAM&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-807-ROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-1" n="1">Would you rise in the church, be stupid and dull,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-2" n="2">Be empty of learning, of insolence full:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-3" n="3">Though lewd and immoral, be formal and grave,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-4" n="4">In flattery an artist, in fawning a slave,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-5" n="5">No merit, no science, no virtue is wanting</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-6" n="6">In him, that's accomplished in cringing and canting:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-7" n="7">Be studious to practise true meanness of spirit;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-8" n="8">For who but Lord Bolton was mitred for merit?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-9" n="9">Would you wish to be wrapped in a rochet── in short,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-ROGP-line-10" n="10">Be as poxed and profane as fanatical Hort.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
